<section
  class="plate studio"
  id="studio"
  data-section="V. Two disciplines, <em>one standard</em>"
  data-page="VI / VI"
>
  <div class="top">
    <span class="l">Studio · Two disciplines</span>
    <span class="r"><em>One standard.</em></span>
  </div>
  <div class="body">
    <div class="col">
      <h3>Product <em>Design</em></h3>
      <p>
        For software founders building considered products. We work end to end from first sketches
        through the design system that keeps the product coherent as it grows.
        <em>We want to be useful early, when the decisions matter most.</em>
      </p>
      <p class="nb">
        Identity · Product surface · Design system · Marketing site. Three to six months, embedded.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <h3>Audio Plugin <em>Design</em></h3>
      <p>
        For plugin developers and audio software companies. We design plugin interfaces that respect
        the workflow of the people using them, with brand and packaging that
        <em>gives the plugin a place in the room.</em>
      </p>
      <p class="nb">
        Plugin GUI · Brand · Packaging · Marketing site · Manual. Six to twelve weeks per plugin.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

